---
import BaseHead from "../../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, CONTACT_EMAIL } from "../../consts";

const effectiveDate = "2026-02-11";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title={`Novi Notes | ${SITE_TITLE}`}
      description="Novi Notes - All-in-one note app for professionals on macOS. Support page and privacy policy."
      lang="en"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header lang="en" />
    <main>
      <article>
        <h1>Novi Notes</h1>
        <p>All-in-one note app for professionals on macOS</p>

        <hr />

        <h2>About the App</h2>
        <p>
          Novi Notes is a native macOS note app designed for professionals.
          Manage daily notes, documents, manuals, post-its, and calendars all in one place.
        </p>

        <h3>Key Features</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Daily Notes &mdash; TODO checklists, work logs, auto carry-over of incomplete tasks</li>
          <li>Block Editor &mdash; 15 block types (text, headings, lists, code, tables, images, audio, Mermaid diagrams, and more)</li>
          <li>Documents & Manuals &mdash; folder organization, version history, PDF/Markdown export</li>
          <li>Post-its &mdash; 20 colors, flexible layouts</li>
          <li>Calendar &mdash; macOS EventKit integration, event CRUD</li>
          <li>Wiki Links & Backlinks &mdash; connect documents together</li>
          <li>Split View &mdash; side-by-side editing</li>
          <li>Menu Bar &mdash; quick access to TODOs and memos</li>
          <li>Voice Recording &mdash; Apple Speech & Whisper speech-to-text</li>
          <li>Backup/Restore, iCloud Sync</li>
          <li>AI Integration via MCP (optional)</li>
        </ul>

        <hr />

        <h2>Support</h2>
        <p>
          If you encounter any issues or have feature requests, please contact us:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email: <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a></li>
          <li><a href="/en/contact">Contact Page</a></li>
        </ul>

        <hr />

        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>Effective date: {effectiveDate}</p>

        <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>
          Novi Notes <strong>does not collect any personal information</strong>.
          All data (notes, documents, settings) is stored locally on your Mac
          and is never transmitted to external servers.
        </p>

        <h3>2. iCloud Sync</h3>
        <p>
          If you enable iCloud sync, your data is stored in your iCloud account
          via Apple's CloudKit. This is managed under Apple's
          <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Privacy Policy</a>.
          The developer has no access to this data.
        </p>

        <h3>3. MCP Integration (Optional)</h3>
        <p>
          When the MCP (Model Context Protocol) feature is enabled, data is
          exchanged with Claude Desktop or Claude Code through the local file system.
          All data is processed locally on your Mac and is never transmitted externally.
        </p>

        <h3>4. Permissions</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Microphone</strong>: Used for voice recording in audio blocks.</li>
          <li><strong>Speech Recognition</strong>: Used for speech-to-text conversion of recordings.</li>
          <li><strong>Calendar</strong>: Used to read and write macOS calendar events.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>All permissions are only used when granted by the user and solely for app functionality.</p>

        <h3>5. Analytics and Advertising</h3>
        <p>Novi Notes does not use any analytics tools, advertising, or trackers.</p>

        <h3>6. Contact</h3>
        <p>
          For privacy-related inquiries, please contact us at
          <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </main>
    <Footer lang="en" />
  </body>
</html>
